---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import hero1 from "../assets/images/hero 1.svg";
import new_hero from "../assets/images/CTA.jpg";
import hero2 from "../assets/images/new_hero1.svg";
import hero3 from "../assets/images/new_hero2.svg";
import proof_funds from "../assets/images/Asset 6.svg";
import personal from "../assets/images/Asset 5.svg";
import business from "../assets/images/Asset 9.svg";
import educational from "../assets/images/Asset 4.svg";
import mortgage from "../assets/images/Asset 7.svg";
import travel from "../assets/images/Asset 8.svg";
import salary from "../assets/images/Asset 9a.svg";
import lpo from "../assets/images/Asset 8a.svg";
---

<Layout title="Home - Contact Credit Limited">
  <main>
    <section
      class="py-12 h-screen bg-money flex items-center bg-cover bg-right md:bg-center bg-no-repeat dark:bg-gray-900"
    >
      <div
        class="grid justify-center max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto md:gap-8 xl:gap-0 md:py-16 md:px-10 lg:px-0 md:grid-cols-12"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center mr-auto place-self-center md:items-start md:col-span-7"
        >
          <h1
            class="text-center max-w-[370px] mb-4 text-xl text-white leading-8 font-extrabold uppercase font-kumbh tracking-tight md:text-left md:max-w-[650px] md:text-4xl md:leading-12"
          >
            CONTACT CREDIT LIMITED
          </h1>
          <h1
            class="text-center max-w-[370px] mb-4 text-white text-xl leading-8 font-extrabold uppercase font-kumbh tracking-tight md:text-left md:max-w-[650px] md:text-4xl md:pb-4 md:leading-12 dark:text-white"
          >
            Empowering your dreams, one loan at a time
          </h1>

          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center animate-wiggle justify-center transition hover:ease-in duration-300 font-kumbh px-5 py-3 mr-3 text-base font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-myGreen bg-myBlue dark:text-white"
          >
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center pt-4 md:mt-0 md:col-span-5 md:flex"
        >
          <!-- <img src={} alt="mockup" class="rounded-lg" /> -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 md:px-12">
        <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
          <div
            class="p-2 border flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center rounded-lg bg-myBlue"
          >
            <h2 class="text-center py-2 font-bold text-white">LOANS</h2>
            <p class="text-md text-white md:pb-2">
              Experience the ease of securing loans for all your needs with our
              hassle-free and customer-centric approach.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4 md:p-6">
          <div
            class="p-2 border flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center rounded-lg bg-greyish"
          >
            <h2 class="text-center py-2 font-bold">COMPETITIVE RATES</h2>
            <p class="text-md md:pb-2">
              Get the Most from Your Money: Our loans come with competitive
              rates, making your financial goals even more achievable.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 md:p-6">
          <div
            class="p-2 border flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center rounded-lg bg-myGreen"
          >
            <h2 class="text-center py-2 font-bold text-white">COME ONBOARD</h2>
            <p class="text-md text-white md:pb-2">
              Unlock the Power of Your Liquidity. Invest with us and seize new
              opportunities for growth and financial success.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="bg-white py-8 flex justify-center items-center dark:bg-gray-900"
    >
      <div
        class="grid justify-center mx-auto max-w-screen-xl md:gap-8 xl:gap-0 md:py-6 md:px-10 lg:px-0 md:grid-cols-12"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-between items-center p-4 md:mt-0 md:col-span-5 md:flex md:items-start"
        >
          <img src={new_hero} alt="mockup" class="rounded-lg md:h-max" />
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col-reverse p-4 justify-center items-center mr-auto place-self-center md:items-start md:col-span-7"
        >
          <p
            class="max-w-2xl font-kumbh px-4 text-md text-justify mb-6 font-light text-gray-600 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            At Contact Credit, we understand that personal aspirations often
            require financial support. Our personalized personal loans provide
            the means to make your dreams a reality. Whether it's a dream
            vacation, home improvement project, or unexpected expenses, we're
            here to help you achieve your goals
          </p>
          <h1
            class="text-center font-kumbh max-w-2xl mb-4 text-xl font-extrabold text-myBlue tracking-tight leading-none md:text-left md:text-2xl xl:text-3xl dark:text-white"
          >
            We Help our Clients To Achieve Their Goals Through Funding
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="bg-white pb-8 flex justify-center items-center dark:bg-gray-900"
    >
      <div
        class="flex flex-col-reverse justify-center mx-auto max-w-screen-xl md:gap-8 xl:gap-0 md:py-6 md:px-10 lg:px-0 md:grid md:grid-cols-12"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col-reverse p-4 justify-center items-center mr-auto place-self-center md:items-start md:col-span-7"
        >
          <p
            class="max-w-2xl font-kumbh px-4 text-md text-justify mb-6 font-light text-gray-600 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg lg:text-xl md:px-0 dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            We offer a diverse portfolio of financial products and services
            tailored to meet the unique needs and aspirations of our clients.
            Whether it's investment opportunities, wealth management, or
            innovative financial strategies, we are dedicated to supporting you
            in achieving your goals.
          </p>
          <h1
            class="text-center font-kumbh max-w-2xl mb-4 text-xl font-extrabold text-myBlue tracking-tight leading-none md:text-left md:text-2xl xl:text-3xl dark:text-white"
          >
            Empowering Your Financial Aspirations
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-between items-center p-4 md:mt-0 md:col-span-5 md:flex md:items-start"
        >
          <img src={hero3} alt="mockup" class="h-full rounded-lg md:h-max" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <hr />
    <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center mb-8 lg:mb-16">
          <h2
            class="mb-4 text-2xl font-kumbh tracking-tight text-center font-extrabold text-myBlue dark:text-white"
          >
            Exceptional Financial Services for Growth
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 font-kumbh sm:text-xl dark:text-gray-400"></p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="space-y-8 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12 md:space-y-0"
        >
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={proof_funds} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Proof of Funds
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh text-justify dark:text-gray-400">
              This service involves the issuance of an official document or
              statement , confirming that a specific individual, business, or
              account holder has the required amount of money available in their
              account to support a particular financial endeavor.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={personal} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Personal Loans
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh text-justify dark:text-gray-400">
              Whatever your goals, our personal loans provide the financial
              flexibility to make them happen. From weddings to home
              improvements, we're here to support your dreams. Apply today and
              take the first step toward achieving your aspirations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={educational} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center font-bold text-myBlue font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Educational Loans
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh text-justify dark:text-gray-400">
              We're here to help you succeed academically. Our student loans
              provide the financial support you need for tuition, books, and
              more. Start your educational journey today.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={mortgage} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Asset Management
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh text-justify dark:text-gray-400">
              Our specialized asset management services drive efficiency and
              growth. Let us optimize your assets for financial success.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={travel} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Travel Loans
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh text-justify dark:text-gray-400">
              Your dream vacation awaits, and our travel loans can take you
              there. Fast, easy, and hassle-free financing for your next
              adventure.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={business} class="w-24" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Business Loans
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh overflow-ellipsis text-justify dark:text-gray-400"
            >
              Our business loans are here to drive your business forward. Fast,
              flexible financing to fuel your growth and success.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={salary} class="w-20" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              Salary Advance
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh overflow-ellipsis text-justify dark:text-gray-400"
            >
              Our salary advance service is here to provide financial support
              when unexpected expenses arise. Get the funds you need quickly and
              hassle-free. We're your solution for financial peace of mind.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="px-4">
            <div
              class="flex justify-center items-center mb-4 w-auto h-auto rounded-full bg-primary-100 lg:h-auto lg:w-auto dark:bg-primary-900"
            >
              <img src={lpo} class="w-16" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 text-xl text-center text-myBlue font-bold font-kumbh dark:text-white"
            >
              LPO Financing
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-gray-600 font-kumbh overflow-ellipsis text-justify dark:text-gray-400"
            >
              Secure the funds you need to fulfill purchase orders with our LPO
              financing. We're your partner in business growth, providing quick
              and reliable financial solutions to meet your procurement needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section
      class="bg-white py-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-center dark:bg-gray-900"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <h4 class="font-extrabold text-myBlue font-kumbh text-2xl p-4">
          Why Choose Us?
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div
        class="grid justify-center mx-auto max-w-screen-xl md:gap-8 xl:gap-0 md:py-6 md:px-10 lg:px-0 md:grid-cols-12"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-between items-center p-4 md:mt-0 md:col-span-5 md:flex md:items-start"
        >
          <img src={hero2} alt="mockup" class="h-full rounded-lg md:h-max" />
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col-reverse p-4 justify-center items-center mr-auto place-self-center md:items-start md:col-span-7"
        >
          <p
            class="max-w-2xl font-kumbh px-4 text-md text-justify mb-6 font-light text-gray-600 lg:mb-8 md:text-lg lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            At Contact Credit, we're not merely a loan company; we're your
            trusted gateway to a robust network of financial services. We take
            pride in offering a wide spectrum of financial solutions that reach
            far beyond the realm of traditional loans. Our extensive network
            encompasses cooperative services that foster collaboration and
            financial growth. We provide avenues for joint ventures, enabling
            you to leverage partnerships for mutual success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .text-gradient {
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-size: 400%;
    background-position: 0%;
  }
  .instructions {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
    background-color: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.4rem;
  }
  .instructions code {
    font-size: 0.875em;
    font-weight: bold;
    background: rgba(var(--accent), 12%);
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.3em 0.45em;
  }
  .instructions strong {
    color: rgb(var(--accent));
  }
  .link-card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
